  "title": "[🌈ENTRY LEVEL | FUN 🌈] EVENT SALES TEAM",
  "description": "<h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li>Represent brands at events, malls, and pop-ups sites</li><li>Connect with customers through fun interactions</li><li>Assist in event operations and setup</li><li>Work closely with team leaders to reach targets</li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Enjoy</strong></h3><ul><li>🚀 Rapid learning & skills development</li><li>😄 Fun, youthful work environment</li><li>📚 Mentorship from experienced leaders</li><li>💸 Weekly incentives + uncapped earnings</li><li>🌍 Exposure to different event types</li></ul><h3><strong>Who we're looking for</strong></h3><ul><li>Friendly, confident, and proactive</li><li>Loves talking to people</li><li>Willing to learn and open to feedback</li><li>Fresh grads and students welcome!</li></ul><p><br /><em>If you’re looking for a job where work feels less like “work” and more like fun, friends, and future opportunities — this is it✨</em></p><p>📩<strong> Apply today — Fun, growth, and endless possibilities are just a click away!</strong></p>",
